<db:section xml:id="introduction">
<db:title>Introduction</db:title>
<db:para>We will explain how to make Qt Quick applications accessible. This can be compared to making web application accessible. You simply need to assign a few properties when creating controls such as buttons in QML.</db:para>
<db:para>The most important property for this purpose is the attached property <db:link xlink:href="qml-qtquick-accessible.xml">Accessible</db:link>.</db:para>
